  heading: Introduction to Virtual Reality
  details: 'A Virtual Reality (VR) Lab introduces students to immersive digital environments
    and interactive technologies.

    It is equipped with VR headsets, controllers,
    and software for hands-on learning experiences.

    The lab helps learners understand
    VR concepts, applications, and real-world use cases across different fields.'
